@NODE 1. "Basics / Functions"


The Packet SMB-Connect contains to programs to connect drives
and printers over an tcp-stack by using NetBIOS.

You can create an amiga-mountlist for any net device and  you
can  mount  this  by  Amiga  "mount"  command  with the first
program smb-handler. The other way using a gui with smb-net.


@{" Copyright " Link 1.1.}
@{" Contents " Link 1.2.}
@{" Requierements " Link 1.3.}
@{" Security " Link 1.4.}
@ENDNODE

