@NODE 3. "SMB-Net"


The documantation is very short because the smb-net  is  only
in test state and if all works than I will create an gui with
mui.


@{" Installation SMB-Net " Link 3.1.}
@{" Tooltypes " Link 3.2.}
@{" Commandline " Link 3.3.}
@{" Errors SMB-Net " Link 3.4.}
@{" Todo (SMB-Net) " Link 3.5.}
